                    Whether you're a fan of classic flavors or adventurous combinations, we have something for everyone.
                    Join us on this sweet journey and indulge in the magic of our ice cream creations!</p>
                  
                    <div class="btnunite">
                    <button class="btn">Products <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></button><button class="howitmade">How it's made <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    
           

                </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 "  style="overflow:clip;height:86.5vh;width:auto;">
                <img src="/images/strawcone2.png" alt="Ice Cream" class="img-fluid rounded icecream" >

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
